import { Input,Grid,Image, Card } from "@nextui-org/react"

export const Hero = () => {
    return(
        <Grid.Container gap={4}>
        <Grid xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={6}>
        {/* <Card
                css={{ p: "$6", padding: "$10", marginTop: "$14" }}
                variant={"bordered"}
              > */}
              <Card ></Card>
        <Input 
            underlined 
            labelPlaceholder="name" 
            color="default" 
          />
          <Input 
            underlined 
            labelPlaceholder="category" 
            color="default" 
          />
          <Input 
            underlined 
            labelPlaceholder="price" 
            color="default" 
          />
           
          </Grid>
         
          <Grid xs={12} sm={6} md={6} lg={6}>
          <Image
              src="form.svg"
              css={{ borderRadius: "$2xl" }}
              alt={"con"}
            />
          </Grid>
      
       
      </Grid.Container>
    )
}
